    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Hyouton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 2 (Spell Level 1)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 14 | <b>Successes:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 2 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 13</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You temporarily freeze the surface of the target square, causing all creatures to lose their Dexterity bonus to Defense. If an affected creature leaves the area, it immediately recovers from this penalty. Creatures not standing on the surface are unaffected.</p>\n\n\n\n",
